definitions.definition: A public building or room for gambling .
examples: He went to the casino every night till 1:00 am.

definitions.definition: A small house; a pleasure house or holiday home , especially in Italy.
A certain Italian card game for two to four players.
Any of certain cards with special meanings in this game.

main_definition: A public building or room for gambling .
secondary_definitions: ( obsolete ) A small house; a pleasure house or holiday home , especially in Italy.
( uncountable ) A certain Italian card game for two to four players.
( countable ) Any of certain cards with special meanings in this game.
